====Pronoun====
{{ja-pos|pronoun|あちら}}

# that way; that [[over there]], [[far away]], in the distance

=====Usage notes=====
* The hiragana spelling ([[あちら]]) is preferred to the kanji spelling ([[彼方]]), which is rarely used.

